_:N00c50b35a3f04defb39a8e96c8feb8b1 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Sue is the Interim Regional Director for the West Midlands, starting the role in July 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She previously served as Director of Teaching Workforce: Candidates, Trainees, Strategy, Portfolio and Analysis at the Department for Education (DfE) and Director, Professional and Technical Education, at the Education and Skills Funding Agency (ESFA).</p>\n\n<p>Sue joined the civil service in 2003 and has also held roles at the:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Department for Transport (DfT)</li>\n  <li>Department for Education</li>\n  <li>Ministry of Housing, Communities &amp; Local Government (MHCLG)</li>\n</ul>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
